## ğŸ›  Development

1. **Clone the repository**:
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/MahmoudGShake/JsonCrack.git
   cd JsonCrack
   ```
2. **Install dependencies**:
   ```sh
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```
3. **Install package in editable mode**:
   ```sh
   pip install -e .
   ```

